entries.journal_entry_description: Osae Meilea, at the Yavin 4 Mining Camp, doesn't like the way one of her competitors is doing business. She has hired you to deliver a warning to one Nagem Dr' Lar. Of course Osae never mentioned exactly what her business is.
entries.task00_journal_entry_description: Warn Nagem Dr' Lar about her interference with Osae Meilea's business.
entries.task02_journal_entry_description: Nagem's guard didn't seem to be too much trouble. Now its time to talk to Nagem and make sure she got the message.
entries.task03_journal_entry_description: You got Nagem Dr' Lar to see things your way. During your conversation you discovered that Osae is really a Hutt operative looking to do some illegal scavenging of remnants of the Death Star.  Go back to Osae and tell her that Nagem agreed to Osae's terms.
